te analyses are needed to\ninfer reliable information on the inflationary Universe.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 16:50:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2023 10:06:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-09"}
