 the bar formation almost completely in\nthick-disc-only models. We find that the Ostriker-Peeble criterion predicts the\nbar instability scenarios in our models better than the\nEfstathiou-Lake-Negroponte criterion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 18:00:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 18 Apr 2023 15:22:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-19"}
