orresponding reference measurements,\nchanged over time by -0.12 ug/m3 (95% CI: -0.13 ug/m3, -0.11 ug/m3) per year.\nThe average bias increases dramatically after 3.5 years. Climate zone is a\nsignificant modifier of the association between degradation outcomes and time.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Oct 2022 14:41:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Oct 2022 00:44:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-28"}
